 thit k thanh lch, n tng ng trong hp g thng sang trng ca nh Travaglini.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1500ml x 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - Gattinara DOCG -Nebbiolo 1500ml','','publish','open','open','','travaglini-il-sogno-vino-da-uve-stramature-nebbiolo-2','','','2016-12-28 15:30:02','2016-12-28 08:30:02','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=309',0,'post','',0),(311,1,'2016-12-13 15:56:41','2016-12-13 15:56:41','<p>Th nhng rt giu khong cht  dnh tng cho loi ru ny sc mu  hung m, mu ca nhng tng ni  bn a. Ru c  trng thnh trong 3 nm vi 2 nm  trong thng g si Slovenia, sau  cn bng 3 thng trong chai. Ru m  hng tri cy , v cht mt m m du vi cu trc tt v m hng khong cht. Kt hp tuyt vi vi tht , tht gia cm, cheese.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chai ru vi dung tch 1,5 lt c thit k thanh lch, n tng ng trong hp g thng sang trng ca nh Travaglini.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1500ml x 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - IL SOGNO -Vino da uve Stramature -Nebbiolo','','inherit','closed','closed','','309-revision-v1','','','2016-12-13 15:56:41','2016-12-13 15:56:41','',309,'http://54.226.229.29/309-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(313,1,'2016-12-13 16:01:43','2016-12-13 16:01:43','Ru c mu  hung. S khc bit c bit trong thnh phn t giu cht st  lm nn loi ru c o vi hng v khng th trn ln. Loi ru ny ch c sn xut trong nhng ma v tt nht. Ru c  trng thnh trong 4 nm, 3 nm  trong thng g si Slovenia , sau  c  cn bng 8 thng trong chai. Ru m  hng v tri cy ha cng hng khong cht. L s kt hp trn tra ca hng v tri cherries, hng hoa hng, cam tho v tiu en. Cht cht mt m, hu v ko di m du. Bo qun  nhit  18-20C, lu tr trn 15 nm\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - Riserva - Gattinara DOCG - Nebbiolo','','publish','open','open','','travaglini-riserva-gattinara-docg-nebbiolo','','','2016-12-13 16:01:43','2016-1