2','<p>L loi ru nh cao kt tinh ca ngh thut lm ru v tinh hoa t lch s, c nhc n t tp xut bn u tin nm 1850 ca tp ch Cocks and Feret , nm 1893 v nm 1908 c nhc n nh biu tng pht trin ca ngnh ru vang. Trong n phm 17 c vinh danh trang trng. Ru mu  ruby mnh m l tng trng cho tui tr v s c ng c o ca hng v tri cy. Rt mnh m - h l cht hng v tri cy en kt hp cng v cay v vani. im c bit ca loi ru ny c th hin bi cu trc rt tt v tao nh, dy ln gia vm ming vi cht cht mm du v hng tri cherry en ha cng cht hng vani. Hu v cn bng ko di trong vm ming.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Medoc - France</li>\r\n</ul>','Chateau LA GRAVETTE LACOMBE 2010 - CRU BOURGEOIS','','publish','open','open','','chateau-la-gravette-lacombe-2010-cru-bourgeois','','','2016-12-18 07:20:22','2016-12-18 07:20:22','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=405',0,'post','',0),(406,1,'2016-12-18 07:20:19','2016-12-18 07:20:19','','chateau-la-gravette-lacombe-2010-cru-bourgeois','','inherit','open','closed','','chateau-la-gravette-lacombe-2010-cru-bourgeois','','','2016-12-18 07:20:19','2016-12-18 07:20:19','',405,'http://54.226.229.29/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Chateau-LA-GRAVETTE-LACOMBE-2010-CRU-BOURGEOIS.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(407,1,'2016-12-18 07:20:22','2016-12-18 07:20:22','<p>L loi ru nh cao kt tinh ca ngh thut lm ru v tinh hoa t lch s, c nhc n t tp xut bn u tin nm 1850 ca tp ch Cocks and Feret , nm 1893 v nm 1908 c nhc n nh biu tng pht trin ca ngnh ru vang. Trong n phm 17 c vinh danh trang trng. Ru mu  ruby mnh m l tng trng cho tui tr v s c ng c o ca hng v tri cy. Rt mnh m - h l cht hng v tri cy en kt hp cng v cay v vani. im c bit ca loi ru ny c th hin bi cu trc rt tt v tao nh, dy ln gia vm ming vi cht cht mm du v hng tri cherry en ha cng cht hng vani. Hu v cn bng ko di trong vm ming.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Medoc - France</li>\r\n</ul>','Chateau LA GRAVETTE LACOMBE 2010 - CRU BOURGEOIS','','inherit','close