 tone typical of sauvignon blanc. A blend of grapefruit with a nice balance of flavor, the finish is smooth with a lingering hint of mango.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 12</li>\r\n 	<li>White</li>\r\n 	<li>13%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>','PASO FINO Sauvignon Blanc','','publish','open','open','','paso-fino-sauvignon-blanc-2','','','2016-12-28 14:09:19','2016-12-28 07:09:19','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=510',0,'post','',0),(511,1,'2016-12-28 14:09:16','2016-12-28 07:09:16','Soft yellow color. Very intense grapefruits citrus nose with notes of melon fruit and sweet floral tone typical of sauvignon blanc. A blend of grapefruit with a nice balance of flavor, the finish is smooth with a lingering hint of mango.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 12</li>\r\n 	<li>White</li>\r\n 	<li>13%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>','PASO FINO Sauvignon Blanc','','inherit','closed','closed','','510-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 14:09:16','2016-12-28 07:09:16','',510,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/511',0,'revision','',0),(512,1,'2016-12-28 14:10:35','2016-12-28 07:10:35','Deep ruby red color. Full rich red fruit aromas of cherry jam, peppery and spicy with sweet green pepper notes. A velvety well balanced acidity with chocolate notes and abundant sweet rounded tannins.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 12</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>','PASO FINO Cabernet Sauvignon','','publish','open','open','','paso-fino-cabernet-sauvignon-2','','','2016-12-28 14:10:38','2016-12-28 07:10:38','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=512',0,'post','',0),(513,1,'2016-12-28 14:10:35','2016-12-28 07:10:35','Deep ruby red color. Full rich red fruit aromas of cherry jam, peppery and spicy with sweet green pepper notes. A velvety well balanced acidity with chocolate notes and abundant sweet rounded tannins.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 12</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>','PASO FINO Cabernet Sauvignon','','inherit','closed','closed','','512-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 14:10:35','2016-12-28 07:10:35','',512,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/513',0,'revision','',0),(514,1,'2016-12-28 14:20:58','2016-12-28 07:20:58','eque from the quechua word \"NIQQUIY\" meanings strenght or vigour of bouth the body and the soul. A great elegant wine with limited edition release and one of Casa Patronales winery\'s pride.\r\nThis wine has a dark red color. On the nose it is a complex and elegant wine, where the black fruits, spices and cassis complement the notes of tobacco due to extended barrel aging. In the mouth it is a bulky wine, very elegant of dense and silky tannins. A buttery start, with notes of dry plums, cherries and smooth chocolate to follow. This wine has a fresh and persistent finish.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>14%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: left; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\" align=\"right\"><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'serif\';\"></span></p>','CASAS PATRONALES NEQUE Cabernet Sauvignon','','publish','open','open','','casas-patronales-neque-cabernet-sauvignon-2','','','2016-12-28 14:21:03','2016-12-28 07:21:03','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=514',0,'post','',0),(515,1,'2016-12-28 14:20:58','2016-12-28 07:20:58','eque from the quechua word \"NIQQUIY\" meanings strenght or vigour of bouth the body and the soul. A great elegant wine with limited edition release and one of Casa Patronales winery\'s pride.\r\nThis wine has a dark red color. On the nose it is a complex and elegant wine, where the black fruits, spices and cassis complement the notes of tobacco due to extended barrel aging. In the mouth it is a bulky wine, very elegant of dense and silky tannins. A buttery start, with notes of dry plums, cherries and smooth chocolate to follow. This wine has a fresh and persistent finish.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>14%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir=\"RTL\" style=\"margin: 0in; margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: left; direction: rtl; unicode-bidi: embed;\" align=\"right\"><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'serif\';\"></span></p>','CASAS PATRONALES NEQUE Cabernet Sauvignon','','inherit','closed','closed','','514-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 14:20:58','2016-12-28 07:20:58','',514,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/515',0,'revision','',0),(516,1,'2016-12-28 14:25:13','2016-12-28 07:25:13','<strong>CABERNET 60%, MALBEC 25%, PETIT SHYRAH 15%</strong>\r\n\r\nThis is a playful blend of distinctive fruits and noble woods, which together make this singular wine. It arose as a unique, special blend, without any ambition other than to represent our efforts. The varieties which achieve the greatest expression in the Maule Valley are here. The secret is that each year the valley expresses itself in a different way, so the blend is an edition limited to each harvest.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>14%</li>\r\n 	<li>Maule Valley/Chile</li>\r\n</ul>','CASAS PATRONALES MIXTURA Cabernet/ Malbec/ Petit Shyrah','','publish','open','open','','casas-patronales-mixtura-cabernet-malbec-petit-shyrah-2','','','2016-12-28 14:25:16','2016-12-28 07:25:16','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=516',0,'post','',0),(517,1,'2016-12-28 14:25:13','2016-12-28 07:25:13','<strong>CABERNET 60%, MALBEC 25%, PETIT SHYRAH 15%</strong>\r\n\r\nThis is a playful blend of distinctive fruits and noble woods, which together make this singular wine. It arose as a unique, special blend, without any ambition other than to represent our efforts. The varieties which achieve the greatest expression in the Maule Valley are here. The secret is that each year the valley expresses itself in a different way, so the blend is an edition limited to each harvest.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li