 in 20hl Slavonian oak barrel, finally 8 months in bottle. This is a unique wine, one finds the essence of the land and its traditions combined with technique and experience.\r\n\r\nIntense garnet red, wine with big structure, with complex and variegated aromas of fruits of the forest and light balsamic scent, with minerality and ripe fruits end.\r\n\r\nServing Temperature: 18/20oC, Shelf life: over 15 years.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>750ml x 6</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>15,5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont/ Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - IL SOGNO -Vino da uve Stramature -Nebbiolo','','inherit','closed','closed','','580-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 15:25:49','2016-12-28 08:25:49','',580,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/581',0,'revision','',0),(582,1,'2016-12-28 15:29:54','2016-12-28 08:29:54','Th nhng rt giu khong cht  dnh tng cho loi ru ny sc mu  hung m, mu ca nhng tng ni  bn a. Ru c  trng thnh trong 3 nm vi 2 nm  trong thng g si Slovenia, sau  cn bng 3 thng trong chai. Ru m  hng tri cy , v cht mt m m du vi cu trc tt v m hng khong cht. Kt hp tuyt vi vi tht , tht gia cm, cheese.\r\n\r\nChai ru vi dung tch 1,5 lt c thit k thanh lch, n tng ng trong hp g thng sang trng ca nh Travaglini.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1500ml x 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - Gattinara DOCG -Nebbiolo 1500ml','','inherit','closed','closed','','309-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 15:29:54','2016-12-28 08:29:54','',309,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/582',0,'revision','',0),(583,1,'2016-12-28 15:32:43','2016-12-28 08:32:43','Rocky and abundant minerals of iron which give the typical reddish color to the indigenous rock. The wine is aged for 3 years, 2 years in Slovenian oak of different origin and size, then rest in the bottle for 3 months.\r\n\r\nA deep pomegranate red wine; medium  bodied wine shows good depth in its red fruit. Soft silky tannins, with a good structure and intense mineral fragrance.\r\n\r\nVol: 1500ml in Travaglini wooden box\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1500ml x 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - Gattinara DOCG -Nebbiolo 1500ml','','publish','open','open','','travaglini-gattinara-docg-nebbiolo-1500ml','','','2016-12-28 15:32:47','2016-12-28 08:32:47','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=583',0,'post','',0),(584,1,'2016-12-28 15:32:43','2016-12-28 08:32:43','Rocky and abundant minerals of iron which give the typical reddish color to the indigenous rock. The wine is aged for 3 years, 2 years in Slovenian oak of different origin and size, then rest in the bottle for 3 months.\r\n\r\nA deep pomegranate red wine; medium  bodied wine shows good depth in its red fruit. Soft silky tannins, with a good structure and intense mineral fragrance.\r\n\r\nVol: 1500ml in Travaglini wooden box\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>1500ml x 1</li>\r\n 	<li>Red</li>\r\n 	<li>13.5%</li>\r\n 	<li>Gattinara Piedmont - Italia</li>\r\n</ul>','TRAVAGLINI - Gattinara DOCG -Nebbiolo 1500ml','','inherit','closed','closed','','583-revision-v1','','','2016-12-28 15:32:43','2016-12-28 08:32:43','',583,'http://54.226.229.29/archives/584',0,'revision','',0),(585,1,'2016-12-28 15:33:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-12-28 15:33:36','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=585',0,'post','',0),(586,1,'2016-12-28 15:33:57','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-12-28 15:33:57','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=586',0,'post','',0),(587,1,'2016-12-28 15:35:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-12-28 15:35:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://54.226.229.29/?p=587',0,'post','',0),(588,1,'2016-12-28 15:36:55','2016-12-28 08:36:55','This wine is produced only in the best vintage. A deep pomegranate red wine; with a delicate fruity and mineral fragrance with hints of cherries, rose, liquorice